        "subject": "LU-10028 obdclass: Export Lustre special mount infomation",
        "message": "LU-10028 obdclass: Export Lustre special mount infomation\n\nSome users need the information about Lustre mount, but the\noutput information exported by '/proc/mounts' is not enough\nespecially for some Lustre special mount flags and options\nsuch as abort_recov, noir, etc.\nThis patch can help to export some Lustre special mount\ninformation via /sys/kernel/debug/lustre/mounts.\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: Ia230b2152305c22b1f4babfb6aa3e9b323a4d49a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
